  <brief_title>β2-agonist Versus Ipratropium Bromide Associated With β2-agonists in Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease Exacerbation</brief_title>
  <official_title>β2-agonist Versus Ipratropium Bromide Associated With β2-agonists in Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease Exacerbation</official_title>
