  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  have known or suspected COPD based on pulmonary function test, arterial blood gas,
             clinical history, physical examination, and chest radiograph

          -  Age over 18 years old.

          -  COPD Exacerbation: FR&gt;25c/min PaCO2&gt;6Kpa PH&lt;7,35 SaO2&lt;90%

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  GCS ≤ 12

          -  hypersensitivity to anticholinergic

          -  severe acidosis

          -  lack of patient cooperation

          -  serious heart arrhythmia
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
